<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.2.1">
<l>tāntam perumai yaṟiyār tūtu</l>
<l>vēntark kāya vēnta rūrpōl</l>
<l>kāntaḷ viralmeṉ kalainaṉ maṭavār</l>
<l>kūntal kamaḻuṅ kūṭa lūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kūṭalūr, where the hair of lovely ladies with soft clothes</l>
<l>And fingers [like] glory lily [petals], scents [the air],</l>
<l>It seems, is the city of the king who became a messenger</l>
<l>For the kings who did not understand their own eminence.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
